               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp>, proprie <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> congressus </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> conventus </t:quote></cit>, deinde <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> nomen festi inter Pascha et Pentecostem medii </t:quote></cit> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">μεσοπεντηκοστή</foreign>), quo praecipua duarum synodorum dioceseos, secundum Canones Apostolorum quotannis habendarum, celebrabatur (de quo vide Ludolfi comm. hist. p. 386, et lexicon aeth. c. 137) <ref cRef="Marc." loc="6,30">Marc. 6,30</ref> <lbl expand="romanae editionis">rom.</lbl> in titulo; <ref cRef="Enc. Mij." loc="18 ">Enc. Mij. 18 </ref>(in Sx. Tubing.: <ref cRef="Sx. Mij." loc="17">Sx. Mij. 17</ref>); Comp. ecclesiast.; Cod. Mus. Brit. XXIX, 52 et XXX, 51 (ubi <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘረክበተ፡ ካህናት፡</foreign>); <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማኅትው፡ ዘረክበ፡ ካህናት፡</foreign> Deg. Etiam <foreign xml:lang="gez">ረክበት፡</foreign>, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘረክበተ፡ ካህናት፡</foreign> (in festum) <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> conventus sacerdotum </t:quote></cit> Cod. Mus. Brit. XXX, 51. </sense>
               
